views.markdown: If you need help with "TrollStore Helper", you can contact opa334, the developer, via e-mail.
opa334 is the maintainer of the package "TrollStore Helper". Please contact them via email for any questions on this version of the package.
If you found a mistake in the depiction or cannot download the package, you can reach out to the maintainer of the "Zonk's Repo" repo, James Linkton Peach.
